    <string name="account_backup_tips3_md_new" tools:ignore="Typos">        For additional security, you can encrypt your key with a password. This key starts with **ncryptsec1** and cannot be used without your password.
        \n\nIf you lose your password, you will not be able to recover your key.
        \n\nPress one of the buttons below to backup your key.
    </string>
